###Responsive tables
Use this pattern when there is not enough space on smaller screen to fit traditional table layout. This pattern requires adding data-* attribute to
each row cell that mimics the column header text. On smaller screens this text is then displays before the cell value, making information easier to read.

<% partial "/layouts/example" do %>
